        <h1>About Pugs</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <p>Pugs are a delightful and charming breed of dog known for their wrinkled faces and playful personalities. They are often referred to as the "clowns" of the dog world due to their comical expressions and lovable nature.</p>

        <img src="pug.jpg" alt="Adorable Pug">
        
        <p>Pugs are small in size but big in heart. They are known for their friendly and affectionate disposition, making them excellent companions for families, singles, and seniors alike. Their small stature and easygoing nature make them well-suited for apartment living.</p>

        <p>These dogs have a distinctive appearance with their wrinkled skin, curled tails, and expressive eyes. They have a short coat that requires minimal grooming but should be kept clean to prevent skin issues in the folds of their face.</p>

        <p>Pugs are known to be sociable and get along well with other pets, making them a great choice for multi-pet households. They thrive on human companionship and love being the center of attention.</p>

        <p>Whether you're a pug owner or just a pug enthusiast, these adorable dogs are sure to bring joy and laughter into your life.</p>
    </main>
